quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,"Aey Nabi, humne hi tumpar yeh Quran thoda thoda karke nazil kiya hai"
  76,24,"Lihaza tum apne Rubb ke hukum par sabr karo, aur in mein se kisi badh-amal ya munkir-e-haq ki baat na maano"
  76,25,Apne Rubb ka naam subh-o-shaam yaad karo
  76,26,"Raat ko bhi uske huzoor sajda raiz ho, Aur raat ke taveel auqat mein uski tasbeeh karte raho"
  76,27,Yeh log to jaldi hasil honay wali cheez (duniya ) se muhabbat rakhte hai aur aagey jo bhaari din aane wala hai usey nazar andaz kardetey hain
  76,28,"Humne hi inko paida kiya hai aur inke jodh bandh mazboot kiye hai, aur hum jab chahein inki shakalon ko badal kar rakh dein"
  76,29,"Yeh ek nasihat hai,ab jiska jee chahey apne Rubb ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar karle"
  76,30,"Aur tumharey chahne se kuch nahin hota jab tak ke Allah na chachey, yaqeenan Allah bada Aleem-o-Haqeem hai"
  76,31,"Apni rehmat mein jisko chahta hai daakhil karta hai, Aur zalimon ke liye usne dardnaak azaab tayyar kar rakkha hai"